      "updated": 1773708328329,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Como os vetores se transformam/originam em/de texto, áudio, vídeo?",
      "fontSize": 36,
      "fontFamily": 8,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Como os vetores se transformam/originam em/de texto, áudio, vídeo?",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "aWQJN7U_oy_30w6D1bHDL",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -73.37279435659866,
      "y": 1427.5880672646438,
      "width": 1386.0003662109375,
      "height": 45,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "ay",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 851673987,
      "version": 187,
      "versionNonce": 101623811,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1773708328329,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Um processo automático de `tokenization` quebra o input em `chunks`.  ",
      "fontSize": 36,
      "fontFamily": 8,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Um processo automático de `tokenization` quebra o input em `chunks`.  ",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "BpSjl-lmFjOWAdssIjeil",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -46.36268278767852,
      "y": 1547.0680902048082,
      "width": 1801.800537109375,
      "height": 45,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b02",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 253923683,
      "version": 248,
      "versionNonce": 1050718115,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1773708328329,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Um modelo de `embedding` transforma os tokens em vetores. Esse modelo \"conhece\" a matriz M.",
      "fontSize": 36,
      "fontFamily": 8,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Um modelo de `embedding` transforma os tokens em vetores. Esse modelo \"conhece\" a matriz M.",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "3u2e_GkKXd_nS9PQS8tEf",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -46.51362164644593,
      "y": 1632.0943325936764,
      "width": 1267.2001953125,
      "height": 90,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b08",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1388764269,
      "version": 218,
      "versionNonce": 315671363,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1773708328329,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Os vetores produzidos estarão em algum lugar do espaço amostral.\n",
      "fontSize": 36,
      "fontFamily": 8,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Os vetores produzidos estarão em algum lugar do espaço amostral.\n",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "wLsHqLC7BslTYGo2SMkKx",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -30.24400150140218,
      "y": 1755.2889960771056,
      "width": 2554.20068359375,
      "height": 45,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b0E",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1686974883,
      "version": 283,
      "versionNonce": 1538719342,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1773714263688,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Agora sim, o modelo de llm, muito basicamente falando, vai calculando o próximo provável token, que são transformados em vetores.",
      "fontSize": 36,
      "fontFamily": 8,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Agora sim, o modelo de llm, muito basicamente falando, vai calculando o próximo provável token, que são transformados em vetores.",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "7-W6y6uQDTIFe3Y5t8xwW",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -98.29359435415813,
      "y": 1841.0096014288126,
      "width": 2039.400634765625,
      "height": 90,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b0K",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 457333069,
      "version": 297,
      "versionNonce": 1165585074,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1773714274391,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Os vetores resultados se transformam em chunks, e por fim no formato do output esperado, usando o mesmo\nmodelo de embedding. O processo reverso basicamente.",
      "fontSize": 36,
      "fontFamily": 8,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Os vetores resultados se transformam em chunks, e por fim no formato do output esperado, usando o mesmo\nmodelo de embedding. O processo reverso basicamente.",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
